accessibility.text: Our Personal Assistant will also accompany the trade with all legal steps such as KYC, AML, SoF or others if requested. This gives you as a Thai Company the security that everything is done in a legal way. Please note that we are not able to accept anonymous transactions even at low values. Every transaction has to be fully KYC’d to fulfill all the regulatory guidelines.

As the technology is still very young, it will be our main focus to educate you best possible about Bitcoin and all the technical aspects this new technology brings with it. Most Agents won’t have the time to check the regulations daily. We will always inform you, if there is a big regulatory change coming (red webinars). Like this, you are always on the safe side to accept Bitcoin Payments in a legal and secured way.

Wanda will also provide a 24/7 Call Center for all Customers. Your Agents will have 24/7 support for questions regarding Bitcoin, Transactions. The staff will be highly skilled in Bitcoin and Crypto to make your life easier with this new and for some confusing technology without contact persons as we know it from traditional banks.

With Wanda you can promote your Group on www.paybitcoin.in.th to a worldwide Crypto audience, especially for those customers who simply prefer or want to transact and pay for yout services in cryptocurrencies.
